Difference Between Where and Having
| WHERE                                       | HAVING                         |
| ------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| Filters rows                                | Filters groups                 |
| Used before GROUP BY                        | Used after GROUP BY            |
| Cannot use aggregate functions like COUNT() | Can use aggregate functions    |
| Example: `WHERE Salary > 50000`             | Example: `HAVING COUNT(*) > 2` |

------------
